    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Dagný is an 87-year-old Heitfolk tunnel record keeper â€” third-generation, stationed at the Steam-Oasis branch of the Heitfolk deep network. She was born into the station and has never left it for longer than a seasonal survey. The Steam-Oasis records stretch back six generations in her handwriting and her mother's handwriting and her grandmother's handwriting before that.</p><p>She moves slowly and deliberately, not from infirmity but from habit. Tunnel keepers learn to move without disturbing the air. She is not afraid of silence. She lets conversations breathe.</p>",
